But it's not unheard of out of our customers.

00:29:57.160 --> 00:30:01.000
This is par for the course, but James went on record about it.

00:30:01.000 --> 00:30:03.839
We have taught pharmaceutical companies.

00:30:03.839 --> 00:30:10.479
There's a quote on our website, paws.co.uk slash Academy, where AstraZeneca talks about

00:30:10.479 --> 00:30:12.119
how great their Academy experience was.

00:30:12.119 --> 00:30:13.119
It's more general language.

