You may have noticed I'm not a pharmacist.

00:30:27.760 --> 00:30:33.400
I'm an educator, and I geeked out on education, but I hope after hearing this, you get a sense

00:30:33.400 --> 00:30:41.439
of what you need to do to successfully transition your colleagues to R or to Python from wherever

00:30:41.439 --> 00:30:43.079
they're coming from.

00:30:43.079 --> 00:30:48.479
These principles work in every circumstance, and if you avoid them, you're going to have

