with, and fit a model that returns this table here.

00:40:39.679 --> 00:40:44.719
And then they can check to see if they did it right, if it looks the same.

00:40:44.719 --> 00:40:53.840
And then they can extend that, changing maybe the variables in the model or whatnot.

